 * <li><b>tooltipShowPercent (Boolean)</b>  Optional true to also show the value as a percent in the tooltip</li>
 * <li><b>tooltipPrefix (String)</b>  Optional a string to append at the beginning of the tooltip value</li>
 * <li><b>tooltipSuffix (String)</b>  Optional a string to append at the end of the tooltip value</li>
 * <li><b>xlabel (String)</b> xAxis label</li>
 * <li><b>ylabel (String)</b> yAxis label</li>
 * <li><b>fill (String)</b>  Optional fill the area (false, origin, start, end) </li>
 * <li><b>maintainAspectRatio (Boolean)</b> Optional true to maintain chart aspect ratio</li>
 * <li><b>beginAtZero (Boolean)</b>  Optional true to start the graph from the origin</li>
 * <li><b>showLine (Boolean)</b>  Optional show the line</li>
 * <li><b>xAxesdisplay (Boolean)</b> show x axes</li>
 * <li><b>yAxesdisplay (Boolean)</b> show y axes</li>
 * <li><b>showxAxesGrid (Boolean)</b> show x axes grid</li>
 * <li><b>showyAxesGrid (Boolean)</b> show y axes grid</li>
 * <li><b>reverseXorder (Boolean)</b> reverse X order</li>
 * <li><b>reverseYorder (Boolean)</b> reverse Y order</li>
 * <li><b>curvedLine (Boolean)</b>  Optional show the line as curve</li>
 * <li><b>lineColor (String)</b>  Optional the color of the line (#224488)</li>
 * <li><b>lineWidth (Integer)</b>  Optional the line width</li>
 * <li><b>lineDashed (String)</b>  Optional draw a dashed line using some predefined styles (style1,style2,style3,style4)</li>
 * <li><b>pointStyle (String)</b> amongst circle, cross, crossRot, dash, line, rect, rectRounded, rectRot, star, triangle</li>
 * <li><b>pointRadius (Integer)</b>  Optional the size of the point radius</li>
 * <li><b>pointColor (String)</b>  Optional the color of the point (#224488)</li>
